{"tid":2209241,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台反共桌遊集資267萬 擬推手機版","createTime":"2020-09-19T13:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T13:39:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"33f37e2c127a172bd7d939b95e3771df2d6c376b","tid":2209241,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T13:33:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200919/2LAXUROA4ZCCLBUBNMXMN7T6ZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200919%2F2LAXUROA4ZCCLBUBNMXMN7T6ZU%2F&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE2hNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=118e5d2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200919%2F2LAXUROA4ZCCLBUBNMXMN7T6ZU%2F&h=2f085e99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200919/2LAXUROA4ZCCLBUBNMXMN7T6ZU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n台反共桌遊集資267萬 擬推手機版<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/876MURInqB-5w-bm0WkwdUJLuY8=/1508x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HW367HK6ZND5TM4HQ5IFRH7U34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F876MURInqB-5w-bm0WkwdUJLuY8%3D%2F1508x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHW367HK6ZND5TM4HQ5IFRH7U34.jpg&h=f13d7d5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以「反中共統戰」為題的台灣桌遊《逆統戰》（圖），在中共越打壓下反越紅，短短一個月內集資1,000萬新台幣（下同，約267萬港元），超出預期100倍。桌遊開發商ESC（台灣境外戰略溝通工作小組）團隊宣佈，遊戲未來將推出手機版。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小粉紅反面宣傳爆紅<br />\n<br />\n遊戲玩家可在該桌遊扮演香港、蒙古、藏族、哈薩克、維吾爾、滿洲、台灣及反賊，透過不同遊戲策略反中。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。：「非常感謝每一個支持者，這是屬於你們的榮耀，謝謝你們給我們繼續走下去的勇氣（與資金）。」<br />\n<br />\n未知是否內媒得悉遊戲越鬧越紅，網上流出「紅岸通信社」的群組對話，提到高層商討後，下令五毛不得再「出征（即惡意洗版及咒罵）」，轉為「絕對不許談論這事，連自己翻牆出去吵都不行」。<br />\n<br />\n嘖嘖網 / 逆統戰官網"},{"pid":"9a0a8894aaec48186417268d23a240f8f16cb3dc","tid":2209241,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20